snippet.title: Meri Bassai | ‡§Æ‡•á‡§∞‡•Ä ‡§¨‡§æ‡§∏‡•ç‡§∏‡•à | Ep - 791 | 24 Jan, 2023 | Nepali Comedy | Surbir, Ramchandra | Media Hub
snippet.description:
Meri Bassai is one of the longest and most popular Nepali comedy serials with 18 Years of broadcasting. Based on rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people, the series represents many political and social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavor. It is aired in Nepal Television at 8:50 PM and in YouTube at 9:30 PM every Tuesday. This show is produced by Media Hub Pvt. Ltd. 

The story is based on the rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people. The show represents many political as well as social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavour.

Production: Media Hub Pvt. Ltd.
Production Advisor: Som Dhital
Direction: Diwakar Bhandari
Editor: Rabin Bhatta
Sub-Editor: Ashok Chaudhary/Sarita Gautam
IT Manager/Publicity Design : Dibash Humagain
Production Manager : Keshav Kaji Baniya
Script Writer: Kunjan Bhattarai/Diwakar Bhandari
Camera: Rahul Rai
Makeup: Pabitra Bhattarai
Title song Writer: Shankar Adhikari 
Music/Singer: Chetan Sapkota

Artists: Laxmi Giri, Keshav Prasad Pandit(Surbir), Ramchandra Adhikari, Surendra K.C, Palpasa Dangol, Niru Khadka, Tika bhakta Jirel,  Lekhant Bhusal, Diwakar Bhandari, Binam Kandel, Madhu Acharya, Ramesh Magar, Sarswoti Fuyal, Dhirendra Chand and many more.
Special Appearance : Kritina Bhandari

composed by Kalyani Koduri.

N Venkateshwara Rao (Naga Shourya) is an youngster whose ambition is to become a famous TV newsreader just like his bedridden father. He works in a TV studio that is owned by Uday (Srinivas Avasarala). Uday is a socially awkward guy and is bad at communicating with women. Venkateswara Rao falls in love with Prabhavathi (Rashi Khanna) few years back when he visits a relative in Vizag. They break-up because of a misunderstanding. The rest of the story is all about what happens when Uday wants to impress upon Prabhavathi.

snippet.title: Women Power | South Superhit Movies | Jyothika, Nayanthara, Keerthy Suresh, Samantha
snippet.description:
Movie:- Madam Geeta Rani (Raatchasi)
Starcast:- Jyothika, Hareesh Peradi, Poornima Bhagyaraj, Sathyan, Nagineedu, Aruldoss

The film is about a headmaster converting a poorly run school into one of the best in the state.

Movie:- Tejasvini (Aramm)
Starcast:- Nayanthara, Sunu Lakshmi, Ramachandran Durairaj, Kitty, Vela Ramamoorthy

A little girl falls into a deep borewell, and her rescue becomes a huge professional and personal challenge for a collector.

Movie:- Mahanati
Starcast:- Keerthy Suresh, Dulquer Salmaan, Samantha, Vijay Deverakonda, Naga Chaitanya, Rajendra Prasad, Bhanupriya, Malavika Nair 

Savitri, the most admired actress from South Indian cinema, goes through various tragic incidents in her personal life. Unable to cope with depression, she eventually becomes an alcoholic.

Movie:- U Turn
Starcast:- Samantha Akkineni, Aadhi Pinisetty, Rahul Ravindran, Bhumika Chawla, Ravi Prakash, Ashish Vidyarthi

The plot revolves around the death of motorists who break a traffic rule at a particular flyover in Hyderabad and the subsequent pinning down of the culprit by an intern journalist and police inspector duo.

snippet.description:
#shorts

üòçOMG! World's Largest River Cruise GangaVilas #shorts 

Finally, PM Narendra Modi inaugurated the world's longest river cruise. But the price of a single trip on this cruise will definitely boggle your brain. This Ganga Vilas named cruise will cover a 3200KM of distance in 50 Days.
This cruise will board from Varanasi, it will reach Bangladesh via Farakka, and will enter India once again completing its first course at Dibrugarh.
This trip will include cultural events like Ganga Aarti, UNESCO heritage sites like Sunderban and Kaziranga National Park, and a lot of other amazing things.
This cruise consists of 18 luxurious suites, where you'll get convertible beds, a French balcony, LED TVs, etc. Apart from this, this ship includes a restaurant, bar, open observation deck for enjoying the sunset, gym, and spa as well. Cultural programs will also be organized for your entertainment.
If we talk about the price of a single ticket, so there is no official disclosure available. But as the tickets for this cruise have got sold out for the next 1.5 years, at the rate of 46.7K USD per suite, it simply indicates that this cruise cannot be afforded by a major portion of Indian citizens. According to the operators, the per day cost for this cruise is said to be around 300 USD only.

snippet.title: How do Fish Breath Underwater? #shorts
snippet.description:
#shorts
For "HUGE" Discount on 3D Animation Course, Call: +91-99830-83303 or Click here üëâüèª https://professorofhow.com

How do Fish Breath Underwater? #shorts 

If someone drowned your head in water, nothing will be more important for you than taking your head out for breathing. But how does a fish spends its whole life inside water? Double tap the screen and let's understand the science behind fish breathing inside water.
A fish consists of two gills on both sides of its head behind its eyes, these gills remain covered by the operculum. The breathing process in fish takes place in 2 steps.
First - The opercula and the mouth of fish both combined work as a pump, which makes water move inside the mouth of the fish through gills and takes it out of the water, this pumping is called buccal pumping.
Second - When water moves through gills, because of the numerous capillaries present in the gills, they work as a filter. These filters absorb oxygen from the water and drain the water and CO2 out of the body.
The absorbed oxygens get bonded with hemoglobin and reach the entire body and completed the breathing process.
However, the fishes like whales and dolphins cannot breathe underwater, they can remain inside the water for a long time without breathing and approach the surface of the water to inhale oxygen.
If you are also interested in creating such cool 3D Animated videos, hit the link given in the pinned comment.
